React is a frontend framework 
which help to build single page application 
using component based structure

////////
Class
> Logical Component
> We can maintain state
> Calling api, writting logics

functional
> Dumb Component
> We cannot maintain state
> Only Use for display purpose

hooks


///////////
State
> Act like a local variable
> Each component can have its own state
> We can update the value of the state
> Any data interaction will happen through state
Props
> Use for transfering the data between nested component
> We cannot update the value of props


parent > child (props)
child > parent (props with callback)

default props
> History (redirection)
> Location (queryParams)
> Match (params)


